{"id":633381,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/01/【立此存照】不晓得你们恐慌什么我有种想/","date":"2020-01-28T12:50:15Z","modified":"2020-01-28T12:51:03Z","title":"【立此存照】“不晓得你们恐慌什么”“我有种想哭的感觉”","content":"<p>近日，有网友twitter上po出一组<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ginkosenpai/status/1221845688675262464\">前后截图</a>：</p>\n<blockquote><p>1月11日，有热心的微博网友在“武汉肺炎”（新型冠状病毒）检测确认后-官方疾病感染数据公布前 就敏锐指出“春运可是来了 ，武汉可是大站”，而在评论区有不少网友指责博主“制造恐慌”，尤其一名武汉本地网友更表示“不晓得你们春运经过武汉几分钟的人恐慌什么”？</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-633420\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"945\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7-159x300.jpeg 159w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7-542x1024.jpeg 542w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7-768x1452.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPTeK2KU8AENUZ7-812x1536.jpeg 812w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月23日，武汉已因“新型冠状病毒”疫情失控，宣布封城。这名当初指责博主“过于恐慌”得到最高点赞的武汉网友已因封城感到了生活方面的不便，“因为囤货时间不会太久，而封城不知到何时”，她表示“我为什么感觉好绝望啊，有种想哭的感觉”。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPVEWrDUcAAAukN.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-633421\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPVEWrDUcAAAukN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPVEWrDUcAAAukN.jpeg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EPVEWrDUcAAAukN-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,39486,39707],"tags":[39595,14933,20821,21827,9363,23966,39719,13381,39708,39648,39611,15083,22718]}